Still others are stung by a desire to do both well and good , says <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Douglas Watson</ENAMEX> , commanding officer of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the Los Angeles Police Department 's</ENAMEX> bunko - forgery division .
