`` It 's not uncommon for these guys to send pictures of themselves or their families to ingratiate themselves to their clients , '' says <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Terree Bowers</ENAMEX> , chief of the major - frauds section of the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX> attorney 's office in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Los Angeles</ENAMEX> .
